Why Should I Rent to Own?

As a consumer, you have many options for purchasing your furniture, appliances, computers, electronics, and smartphones. This can seem a bit overwhelming, but we can help. Here‚Äôs what you need to know about the benefits of rent to own at Rent-A-Center:


Brand Recognition

Rent-A-Center has the brand names you know and trust, including Acer, Ashley Furniture, Dell, Frigidaire, GE, Lenovo, LG, Microsoft, Samsung, Sony, and others. These companies have been selected based on their long, distinguished track records of quality, durability, style, and innovation, which means we carry only the best rental electronics, appliances, computers, furniture, and smartphones.


Instant Gratification, No Worries

With rent to own, you can enjoy big-ticket items from brands like Ashley, Samsung, and Frigidaire without paying the full price up front. Rent-A-Center offers a  Worry-Free Guarantee , so you can take home that smart TV, sectional, dining room set or laptop knowing that you are in control with flexible payment options, Payment Freeze Assurance, free repairs, and more. **


Better Than a Credit Card

When you rent to own, you pay as you go. Your rental application doesn‚Äôt require a credit check, no credit is extended, and no debt is incurred. Rent-A-Center doesn‚Äôt lock you into long commitments, and you can cancel anytime. **Enjoy brands like Ashley, Samsung, and Frigidaire on any budget with rent to own at Rent-A-Center, without relying on credit. 

















